![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-mine-blast-death-toll-rises-to-90-beijing-orders-crackdown-as-rescue-ops-continue-top-developments/articleshow/131279386.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T17:50:24+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131279401,imgsize-1356079.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Fast-developing emergency': 1 killed, several injured after fire, explosions at New York City Shipyard]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131278170.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A devastating fire at a New York City shipyard ignited two powerful explosions, claiming one life and injuring at least 36, including brave firefighters and first responders.  The "complex, fast-developing emergency" saw crews battling flames late into the night after the blasts rocked the area. Investigations into the cause are underway.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fast-developing-emergency-1-killed-several-injured-after-fire-explosions-at-new-york-city-shipyard/articleshow/131278170.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fast-developing-emergency-1-killed-several-injured-after-fire-explosions-at-new-york-city-shipyard/articleshow/131278170.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T16:45:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131278341,imgsize-634314.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Uganda confirms 3 new Ebola cases as WHO warns against underestimating outbreak risk]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131277784.cms"