<dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131273782,imgsize-64942.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Over 80 killed in gas explosion at coal mine in China’s Shanxi province]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131272434.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A devastating gas explosion at the Liushenyu coal mine in northern China's Shanxi province has claimed the lives of at least 90 miners. The blast occurred Friday evening, with carbon monoxide levels reportedly exceeding limits prior to the incident. Rescue operations are ongoing as President Xi Jinping has ordered a full-scale rescue and a thorough investigation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-coal-mine-blast-several-killed-after-gas-explosion-in-shanxi-rescue-operations-for-trapped-under-way/articleshow/131272434.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-coal-mine-blast-several-killed-after-gas-explosion-in-shanxi-rescue-operations-for-trapped-under-way/articleshow/131272434.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T10:47:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131272663,imgsize-1326564.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[London stabbing: Five men injured in violent altercation, one arrested]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131276728.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/london-stabbing-five-men-rushed-to-hospital-after-violent-altercation-one-arrested/articleshow/131276728.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/london-stabbing-five-men-rushed-to-hospital-after-violent-altercation-one-arrested/articleshow/131276728.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T14:49:31+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131276817,imgsize-131258.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Poor thing': Iran mocks Donald Trump as viral buffalo resembling him loses appetite]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131271775.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran's official account in Russia shared a viral video of a Bangladeshi albino buffalo resembling Donald Trump, claiming the animal lost its appetite due to the comparison amid ongoing US-Iran conflict. The buffalo, named 'Donald Trump', has become a local attraction ahead of Eid al-Adha festivities.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/poor-thing-iran-mocks-donald-trump-as-viral-buffalo-resembling-him-loses-appetite/articleshow/131271775.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/poor-thing-iran-mocks-donald-trump-as-viral-buffalo-resembling-him-loses-appetite/articleshow/131271775.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T10:13:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131272164,imgsize-857857.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Revenge matter of time': IRGC-trained Iraqi arrested over assassination plot against Donald Trump's daughter Ivanka]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131271352.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[An IRGC-trained operative, allegedly seeking revenge for Qasem Soleimani's death, was arrested in Turkey and extradited to the US. Mohammad Baqer Saad Dawood Al-Saadi is accused of plotting to assassinate Ivanka Trump, even possessing a blueprint of her Florida home. He reportedly made threats against Americans online.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/revenge-matter-of-time-irgc-trained-iraqi-arrested-over-assassination-plot-against-donald-trumps-daughter-ivanka/articleshow/131271352.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/revenge-matter-of-time-irgc-trained-iraqi-arrested-over-assassination-plot-against-donald-trumps-daughter-ivanka/articleshow/131271352.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T08:49:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131271486,imgsize-858080.cms"/></item></channel></rss>